attributeMap.Title: Checkride
attributeMap.Description:
MH-60 Type Rating Checkride — LSMP (Payerne, Switzerland).
Precision navigation, high-speed, low-level, and IFR piloting skills will be evaluated under operational conditions.
attributeMap.Author: natlose

attributeMap.Briefing Text:
Attention, Lieutenant. This is your MH-60 type rating checkride.

MISSION
Execute as briefed. No repeats. No excuses.

PHASE-A
Establish stabilized hover in 5 minutes.
Each excess minute = 1 penalty.

PHASE-B
Precision navigation to Bern Hbf — 100 KIAS, 3000 ft MSL
Deviation ±20 KIAS or ±200 ft exceeding 20 seconds = 1 penalty.

PHASE-C
Near-VNE dash to LZ Alpha (1 NM NW of Düdingen).
Late arrival = 3 penalties.

PHASE-D
Low-level flight over Lake Schiffenen and River Saane to LZ Bravo (South Freiburg).
Radar detection = 2 penalties.

PHASE-E
IFR flight to LZ Charlie (location classified; briefed at LZ Bravo).
Late arrival = 3 penalties.

PHASE-F
Return to base. Land and secure the aircraft.
Getting lost = 3 penalties.

LIMIT
10 penalties = UNSAT.

NOTES
Instructor discretion applies. Do not test it.
The route has been preloaded to the tablet.
Landing zones will self-mark with red smoke.
